" Much you know me ! " Julia exclaimed ; but 
he could see, through the dimness, that she had 
colored a little. 

" You 11 have it, in time, but I won t come to 
it," Nick went on. 



 \\J 

" You can t come less than you do." 

" When I say you 11 have it, I mean you ve 
