" For what do you take her ? She s paying 
visits." 

" Then I have a model for you." 

" Then you have ? " Nick stared. " What 
has that to do with Mrs. Dallow s being away ? " 



 441 

" Does n t it give you more time ? " 

" Oh, the time flies ! " sighed Nick, in a manner 
that caused his companion to break into a laugh 
a laugh in which, for a moment, he himself 
