As an individual, surely not; I- seem to my 
self to have been all the while rendering her ser 
vices. I said I disliked tea-party ranters, and so 
I do ; but if my estimate of her powers was below 
the mark she has more than punished me." 

" What has she done ? " asked Nick. 



442  

" She has become interesting, as I suppose you 
know." 

" How should I know ?" 

