had, at Nick s request, not looked at his work 
the day before. He fell back, glad to rest, and 
put down his palette and brushes. 

11 Ah, bien, c est tape!" Miriam cried, as she 
stood before the easel Nick was pleased with 
her ejaculation, he was even pleased with what 
he had done ; he had had a long, happy spurt and 
