of his late celebrated relative. He rejoined 
quickly, but rather vaguely : " Ah, yes, I remem 
ber that great man s ideas ; " and then he went 
on : " May I ask if you know it, the fact that we 
are talking of, through Julia or through Nick ? " 



 519 

" I know it from both of them," 

" Then, if you re in their confidence, may I 
further ask whether this undertaking of Nick s 
is the reason why things seem to be at an end 
