after a moment she went straight over to the row 
of stacked canvases and exposed several of them 
to the light. " Why did you say you wished to 
go to the theatre to-night ? " her companion con 
tinued. 

Still the girl was silent ; then she exclaimed, 
with her back turned to him and a little tremor 
