to see you to-day, to tell you my news and take 
leave of vou." 



6; 8  

" Take leave ? Are n t you coming to-mor 
row ? " 

" Oh, yes, I shall see you through that. But 
I shall rush away the very moment it s over." 

" I shall be much better then really I shall," 
the girl said. 

" The better you are the worse you are." 

Miriam returned his gaze with a beautiful char 
