bad." 

"The worse you are the better you are!" 
laughed Sherringham. " You re a kind of de 
vouring demon." 

"Not a bit! It s you." 

"It s I? I like that." 

" It s you who make trouble, who are sore and 
suspicious and supersubtle, not taking things as 
