Yes, I ve got one," the girl went on, " though I 
do paint my face and practice my intonations. 
If what you are going to do is good for you I m 
very glad. If it leads to good things, to honor 
and fortune and greatness, I m enchanted. If it 
means your being away always, forever and ever, 






 6/9 

of course that s serious. You know it I 
need n t tell you I regard you as I really don t 
