do say them. I ve heard many more than I ve 
repeated to you." 

" It s you yourself, then, indignant and sym 
pathetic, who are the martyr," observed Peter, 
who wanted greatly to be kind to her. 

" Oh, I don t care ! " she answered, coloring in 



718 THE TKAGIC MUSE. 

response to this ; and she continued, to Peter : 
" Don t you think one can do as much good by 
