" In the dark ? " his sister demanded. 

"The obscurity, my dear child, of your own as 
pirations, your mysterious ambitions and plastic 
visions. Are n t there some heavyish shadows 
there ? " 

"Why, I never cared for politics." 

" No, but you cared for life, you cared for so- 



 

ciety, and you have chosen the path of solitude 
and concentration." 

" You horrid boy ! " said Biddy. 

