way she does for you ! " 

"It s rather cruel, isn t it," said Miriam, "to 
deprive people of the luxury of calling one an 
actress as they d call one a liar ? I represent, 
but I represent truly." 

"Mr. Sherringham would marry you to-morrow 
there s no question of ten years!" cried Mrs. 
