" Manage me ? " The girl s inflection was 
droll ; it made Sherringham change color. 

" I mean I 11 give you a larger life than the 
largest you can get in any other way. The stage 
is great, no doubt, but the world is greater. It s 
a bigger theatre than any of those places in 
the Strand. We ll go in for realities instead of 



774  

fables, and you 11 do them far better than you do 
