was on a perfectly definite occasion. That occa 
sion was the presence in my studio of a dishev 
eled actress." 

"Oh, Nick, she has not thrown you over!" 
Biddy protested. " She has not I have proof." 

Nick felt, at this direct denial, a certain stir of 
indignation, and he looked at his sister with mo 
